      "widgets_values": [
        "# Gummy wildcard workflow\n\n**Every generation auto-saves its prompt.** Random Prompts feeds BOTH the image and the Save Prompt to Wildcard node. With auto_save = on and mode = numbered, each run writes a new file: gummy_00001.txt, gummy_00002.txt, ...\n\n**Do this once:**\n1. Install the Dynamic Prompts extension (Manager) + the ComfyUI-WildcardSaver node.\n2. RESTART ComfyUI after installing/updating nodes (custom nodes load at startup).\n\nUses your qwen unet/clip/vae + gummycandy LoRA. 20 steps, cfg 4, euler/simple, shift 3.1."
